resources.string: Welcome! I am being held here against my will, and while you and I are both stuck here you might as well adventure into my other tab to find out more about this app. See you soon!

Hello everyone, some big news that I am super excited for is that Treyarch is coming out with a whole new CoD. Its been a minute since we have seen a game from Treyarch, but they are bring back all of our favorites with zombies and 4 very common multiplayer maps that are fan favorites. I hope you are just as excited as I am to get back into a CoD made by Treyarch!
